---
title: Beef & Pepper Enchiladas with Pico de Gallo & Lime Crema
description: Saucy, smothered, hearty, and delicious: This enchilada bake has everything! You’ll start by wrapping tortillas around a filling of spiced ground pork and sautéed bell pepper, then coating the bundles with a healthy glug of zesty, tomatoey sauce and a sprinkle of Mexican cheese. Bake until piping hot and bubbly, then top with lime crema and pico de gallo and dig into all that deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/633c638d5b11944a13030fd5-0d5799af.jpg
